          "reviewBody": "This is not a school; this is a cheating business they have opened up in the Kolkata Newtown branch. When I went to the school for my son, they asked me to block a seat with 10,000. And they mentioned it is refundable if the child is not admitted to the school. I had to cancel the plan and informed the school before the new session started. I asked for a refund; they initially told me they had initiated the refund, but till today I have not received it. Now, the school does not even let me talk to any of their admin staff, principal, or management staff. Fread school; do not engage with this kind of institute that does not follow ethical practice.",
